name anvil toast flow
navigate to http://127.0.0.1:5173
type alice@company.com into the email field
type platform into the team field
click Sign in
click Tasks
type Draft release notes for v0.2.1 into the new-task field
click Add task
assert Added: Draft release notes for v0.2.1 is visible
wait 2500
assert Added: Draft release notes for v0.2.1 is not visible
assert Draft release notes for v0.2.1 is visible
